Class VenueInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.venuemaps.VenueInfo

  • public class VenueInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the outline information of a venue. A VenueInfo can be used to get the name and bounding box of a venue.
